import React, { useRef } from 'react'

const CreateToDo = () => {
    const inputRef = useRef()
  return (
    <form className='AddTodo' onSubmit={console.log("Submited")}>

        <select onChange={(e) => console.log(e.target.value)}>

        <button type='submit' aria-label='Create a ToDo' onClick={() => inputRef.current.focus()}>AAAAAA</button>

}

export default CreateToDo
